title: DAN MORGENSTERN REMEMBERS RUBY BRAFF, PART TWO (Dec. 15, 2017)
fulltitle: DAN MORGENSTERN REMEMBERS RUBY BRAFF, PART TWO (Dec. 15, 2017)
description: A multi-faceted portrait of the marvelous and "eccentric" Ruby Braff, among friends and associates -- by Dan Morgenstern, who knew him well over perhaps fifty years, from Boston days to his final time in a Cape Cod hospice, a very touching story.  Recorded by Michael Steinman at Dan's New York City apartment on December 15, 2017.
